#1,#2]]&,Characters[s],Range[2,StringLength[s]]]]\"\>"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"\<\"ReverseEachWord\"\>", 
    "\[Rule]", "\<\"FizzBuzz[n_Integer] /; n > 0 := Replace[Range[n], {x_ /; \
