/; Mod[x, 5] == 0 :> \\\"buzz\\\"}, 1]\"\>"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{"\<\"RomanSubstitutionWords\"\>", 
    "\[Rule]", "\<\"PairsAddToHundred[inputList_List] := SortBy[Sort /@ \
