Range[PrimePi[cutoff]];\\n  hm = Mod[half, #] & /@ primes;\\n  Do[\\n   \
If[And @@ MapThread[Mod[#1 + x, #2] != 0 && Mod[#1 - x, #2] != 0 &, {hm, \
primes}],\\n    Return[x]],\\n   {x, 1, Infinity}]\\n ]\\n```\"\>", 
