{}]\\n]\\n```\"\>", 
   ",", "\<\"```wolfram\\nQueenGraph[dims:{__Integer}] := Module[{nodes, \
positions, n, edges, posToIndex},\\n  nodes = Tuples[Range /@ dims];\\n  n = \
