positions, but letters jumped over is 12 (13 - 1 = 12). Let me verify: b=1, \
o=14 (0-indexed). |14-1| = 13, minus 1 = 12. And 12+0+3+0 = 15. Let me check: \
o=14, s=18, |18-14|-1=3. s=18, t=19, |19-18|-1=0. So each step contributes \
Max[Abs[diff]-1, 0].\\n\\n```wolfram\\nOneFingerDistance[s_String?LowerCaseQ] \
:= Total[Max[# - 1, 0] & /@ Abs[Differences[ToCharacterCode[s]]]]\\n```\>\"", 
