\\\"bb\\\". Let me check if single letter words should match - a word that \
begins and ends with the same letter and is one character long does begin and \
end with that letter. Let me look at the examples: \\\"bib\\\", \\\"bob\\\" \
are there but no single letter \\\"b\\\". Let me check WordList for single \
letters.\\n\\nActually, let me handle both \
