=#2]&,\\n{seq,Most[chars],Rest[chars]}]]]]//Sort\\n]\\n```\>\"", 
     ",", "\"\<```wl\\nTriangularSums[value_Integer?Positive] := \
Module[{tmax, triangulars, result = {}},\\n  tmax = Floor[(-1 + Sqrt[1 + 8 \
