- 2 n (n . (# - a)) &, pts]\\n    ]\\n  ]\\n]\\n```\>\"", 
     ",", "\"\<```wolfram\\nKnightPoints[image_] := Module[{data, dims, \
blackPositions, knightMoves, knightSet, redPixels, result},\\n  data = \
