   ",", "\<\"PrimePalindromePi[n_Integer] := Module[{palindromes, d, half, \
maxD, result = {}},\\n  If[n < 2, Return[0]];\\n  (* Generate all palindromic \
numbers up to n *)\\n  (* Single digit palindromes: 1-9 *)\\n  maxD = \
