   ",", "\<\"LatticeBallCount[r_ /; 0 < r <= 200] := Module[{r2, count = 0, \
n, rem, zmax},\\n  r2 = r^2;\\n  n = Floor[r];\\n  Do[\\n    rem = r2 - x^2 - \
