sequence."|>, 
       "Single-Digit Numbers" -> <|
        "Description" -> 
         "List the numbers up to <i>n</i> that can be written with a single \
digit in base <i>b</i>."|>, 
       "Smallest Word Number" -> <|
        "Description" -> 
         "Find the smallest integer whose name in English words is of a \
